ation of centrals and satellites with group\nfinders systematically lowers differences between satellite and central\ngalaxies at a level that is comparable to current measurement uncertainties. To\nimprove constraints, the impact of group finding methods will have to be\nforward modeled via mock catalogs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Aug 2017 18:00:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 14:22:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-10"}
